videos.headline: Gunnell throws dart to Johnson for the Arizona TD
videos.description: Grant Gunnell throws a seam to Jalen Johnson in the back of the end zone for the 8-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Gunnell throws dart to Johnson for the Arizona TD) 2019/10/26

videos.headline: Tremayne makes one-handed TD grab
videos.description: Stanford's Brycen Tremayne goes up and makes the phenomenal one-handed touchdown catch.

videos.headline: Tate pump fakes then takes off for long TD run
videos.description: Arizona QB Khalil Tate fakes the throw then shows off the speed for the 57-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Fehoko hauls in the pass, dives in for the TD

videos.headline: Stanford WR holds on and stays in bounds for TD
videos.description: Stanford WR Simi Fehoko climbs the ladder and barely holds on to give his team in the lead 38-31.
